---
layout: page.njk
title: "About Us - HIT Startup Club"
activePage: about
permalink: "about.html"
---
<main class="flex flex-col w-full pt-16">
<section class="relative w-full py-24 md:py-32 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-background-light overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-mesh z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-60"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-text-main mb-6 gradient-underline inline-block pb-4">
                    About Us
                </h1>
<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mt-8 text-text-main font-jp">
                    学生の熱量を、社会を変える力に。
                </p>
<p class="mt-6 text-lg text-text-sub leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto font-jp">
                    広島工業大学起業部は、テクノロジーとアントレプレナーシップを融合させ、
                    広島から世界へインパクトを与えるイノベーションを創出する学生コミュニティです。
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-white relative">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 font-jp">Core Values</h2>
<p class="text-text-sub font-jp">私たちが大切にしている3つの価値観</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-primary">terminal</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Technology-First</h3>
<p class="text-text-sub font-jp text-sm leading-7">
                            アイデアだけで終わらせない。プログラミング、AI、ハードウェア開発など、工大生ならではの技術力を武器に、実際に動くプロダクトを作り上げる「実装力」を重視します。
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-cyan-accent">rocket</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Entrepreneurial Spirit</h3>
<p class="text-text-sub font-jp text-sm leading-7">
                            失敗は学習のプロセスです。リスクを恐れず挑戦し、自らの手で道を切り拓く起業家精神を持ち続けます。ビジネスモデルの構築から資金調達まで実践的に学びます。
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all group">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-indigo-500">groups</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 font-display">Community Driven</h3>
<p class="text-text-sub font-jp text-sm leading-7">
                            一人では成し遂げられないことも、チームなら可能になる。学部・学科を超えた多様な仲間と協力し、地域企業や卒業生とも連携しながら、オープンなコミュニティを築きます。
                        </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-background-alt relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute -left-20 top-20 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-16">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/3 flex flex-col items-center">
<div class="relative w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg mb-6">
<img alt="{{ site.president.role }} {{ site.president.nameEn }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="{{ site.president.photo }}"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-jp">{{ site.president.name }}</h3>
<p class="text-primary text-sm font-bold tracking-wide uppercase mt-1">{{ site.president.role }}</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl text-gray-200 mb-4 select-none">format_quote</span>
<h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-jp mb-6 leading-snug">
                            {{ site.president.headline | safe }}
                        </h3>
<div class="space-y-4 text-text-sub font-jp leading-relaxed">
{% for msg in site.president.messages %}
<p>{{ msg }}</p>
{% endfor %}
</div>
<div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 flex justify-end">
<div class="font-en text-xl italic text-gray-400 font-serif">{{ site.president.nameEn }}</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-20 bg-background-light border-y border-gray-100">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-12">
{% for stat in site.stats %}
<div class="text-center">
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br {{ stat.gradient }} mb-2">{{ stat.value }}</div>
<div class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 font-jp uppercase tracking-wider">{{ stat.label }}</div>
<div class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 font-jp">{{ stat.labelJp }}</div>
</div>
{% endfor %}
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-white">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 font-jp">Our Journey</h2>
<p class="text-text-sub font-jp">これまでの歩みと成長</p>
</div>
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-100"></div>
{% for event in site.timeline %}
<div class="relative flex items-center justify-between {% if not loop.last %}mb-16{% endif %} w-full {% if event.side == 'right' %}flex-row-reverse{% endif %}">
{% if event.side == 'left' %}
<div class="w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-main">{{ event.title }}</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-sub mt-2 font-jp">{{ event.description }}</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-{{ event.color }} z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
<div class="w-5/12 pl-8">
<span class="text-{{ event.color }} font-bold font-display text-lg">{{ event.date }}</span>
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="w-5/12 text-left pl-8">
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-main">{{ event.title }}</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-text-sub mt-2 font-jp">{{ event.description }}</p>
</div>
<div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white border-4 border-{{ event.color }} z-10 shadow-sm"></div>
<div class="w-5/12 pr-8 text-right">
<span class="text-{{ event.color }} font-bold font-display text-lg">{{ event.date }}</span>
</div>
{% endif %}
</div>
{% endfor %}
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-jp">Ready to Join Us?</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-text-sub mb-10 font-jp">
                    私たちと一緒に、新しい一歩を踏み出しませんか？<br/>
                    見学・入部相談はいつでも受け付けています。
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
<a href="https://line.me/ti/g2/I4hPOfn28NLrMfHr6Uln_BRtiXHN4ewwg5sbPw?utm_source=invitation&utm_medium=link_copy&utm_campaign=default" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-gradient text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2" style="text-decoration:none;">
<span>Apply Now (入部申し込み)</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
<a href="contact.html" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-text-main font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-block">
                        Contact Us
                    </a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
